#: ../../source/info/port.rst:124
msgid "常见端口扫描技术"
msgstr "Common Port Scanning Techniques"

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:127
msgid "全扫描"
msgstr "Full Scan"

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:128
msgid "扫描主机尝试使用三次握手与目标主机的某个端口建立正规的连接，若成功建立连接，则端口处于开放状态，反之处于关闭状态。"
msgstr ""
"The scanning host attempts to establish a normal connection to a target port "
"through the TCP three-way handshake. If the connection is established, the "
"port is open; otherwise, it is closed."

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:130
msgid "全扫描实现简单，且以较低的权限就可以进行该操作。但是在流量日志中会有大量明显的记录。"
msgstr ""
"A full scan is easy to implement and can be performed with relatively low "
"privileges, but it leaves a large number of obvious records in traffic logs."

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:133
msgid "半扫描"
msgstr "Half-open Scan"

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:134
msgid "半扫描也称SYN扫描，在半扫描中，仅发送SYN数据段，如果应答为RST，则端口处于关闭状态，若应答为SYN/ACK，则端口处于监听状态。不过这种方式需要较高的权限，而且现在的大部分防火墙已经开始对这种扫描方式做处理。"
msgstr ""
"A half-open scan is also called a SYN scan. It sends only a SYN segment. If "
"the response is RST, the port is closed; if the response is SYN/ACK, the port"
" is listening. This method requires higher privileges, and most modern "
"firewalls already handle this type of scan."

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:137
msgid "FIN扫描"
msgstr "FIN Scan"

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:138
msgid "FIN扫描是向目标发送一个FIN数据包，如果是开放的端口，会返回RST数据包，关闭的端口则不会返回数据包，可以通过这种方式来判断端口是否打开。"
msgstr ""
"A FIN scan sends a FIN packet to the target. An open port returns an RST "
"packet, while a closed port returns no packet. This behavior can be used to "
"determine whether a port is open."

#: ../../source/info/port.rst:140
msgid "这种方式并不在TCP三次握手的状态中，所以不会被记录，相对SYN扫描要更隐蔽一些。"
msgstr ""
"This method is outside the TCP three-way handshake state flow, so it is not "
"recorded in the same way and is somewhat stealthier than a SYN scan."

